text: The Estadio Municipal Claudio Suárez is a multi-use stadium located in Texcoco, State of Mexico, Mexico. It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium for Real Cuautitlán. The stadium has a capacity of 4,000 people. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Multi- purpose stadiums in Mexico Municipal Claudio Suarez Category:Athletics (track and field) venues in Mexico
